  "Description": {
    "English": "A highly refined food product, created in the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span>. It has both the identifying shapes and aromas of an actual food item, in stark contrast with conventional nutrition paste or pellets.<br><br>Food such as this can be <span class=\"name name-stellar\">highly valuable</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>制作的精制食品。这些食物在形状和气味上与真实的食品极为相似，和传统的营养剂或胶囊截然不同。<br><br>这种食物可能拥有<span class=\"name name-stellar\">极高的价值</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>生成的高度精制食品。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>生成的精製食品，具有真正食物的外形和味道，和一般的營養糊或營養丸截然不同。<br><br>這種食物可能<span class=\"name name-stellar\">極為有價值</span>。"
  },
